Digital Services
Paytm offers on the Paytm Platform certain digital products such as purchase of movie tickets, bus tickets, hotel reservations, flight tickets, tickets to amusement or theme parks, coupon redemption services etc. Further, Paytm may facilitate on its Platform, services from its related entities such as the purchase of prepaid recharges for mobile, DTH, toll and data card etc.
The terms and conditions in relation to digital products and bill payments set out below are applicable to and binding on You in conjunction with these SSOID terms and conditions. Each SSOID term or condition is applicable to and binding on You, for any of Your activities on the Paytm Platform, even if such term or condition is not specifically reproduced herein below.
The terms ‘Agreement’ or ‘T&Cs’ mentioned herein below includes the terms and conditions in relation to digital products set out below, bill payments, the SSOID terms and conditions as well as other service-specific terms and conditions in relation to Paytm Services or Paytm Platform.
For various facilities and technology features made available on Paytm Platform, please note that a convenience fee may be chargeable from you by Paytm or its related entities providing respective services. For e.g. for adding money to wallet using the Paytm Platform the following charges will be levied by the online payment aggregator viz., Paytm Payments Services Limited :
