Charges: Recharges and Bill Payments on Paytm
Maintenance charges in the nature of a) convenience fee and/or b) platform fee, will be applicable for utilizing recharges and bill payments services on Paytm Platform, e.g. for paying electricity bill, mobile recharge, etc.
a) Convenience Fee
Convenience fee is a fee charged towards covering the cost of transactions (Inclusive of GST). This fee is applicable on certain payment methods such as debit card, credit cards, net banking etc.
